<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">更新了 GUI 精灵图。</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">equipment</TextBox> 文件夹现在上移一级，即 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">models/equipment/</TextBox> 现在移动到 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">equipment/</TextBox>。</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">broken_elytra</TextBox> 模型和纹理现在重命名为 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">elytra_broken</TextBox>。</Paragraph></ListItem>
